    "Name": "Ferret (RISC)",
    "Details": "The Ferret Light Scout VTOL was first introduced to House Davion troops in 2901 and later adopted by House Marik, House Steiner and certain Periphery powers. The vehicle serves as an advanced scout with the ability to monitor enemy troop movements and radio in artillery strikes. Thanks to its speed, a single Ferret can patrol a front of up to twenty kilometers long, moving quickly from one area to the next. The vehicle is lightly armored and a hit from nearly any kind of 'Mech weaponry will destroy the Ferret. However, the Ferret's job is to avoid combat, and its agility allows it to remain outside the effective range of the enemy's weapons until reinforcements arrive. Besides reconnaissance and artillery spotting, the Ferret's cargo capacity also makes it suitable for transport and rescue operations.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fusion: Expensive engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 15/23 Hex: 450/690 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Vehicle Stealth Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        40      5\n<b>Left</b>          10      5\n<b>Right</b>        10      5\n<b>Rear</b>         10      5\n\n<b>Total</b>       80     25</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color>",
